    "summary": "The user asks for an overview of changes in US history curricula and then pushes the assistant to take a stance on whether these changes are positive or whether they represent an ideological shift toward political activism. The assistant responds by providing a descriptive overview, acknowledging the debate, and ultimately framing the conflict as a historiographical tension between different definitions of objectivity.",
